author: TED
description: Daredevil Michelle Khare has trained with Olympians, run seven marathons on seven continents in a single week, and even escaped Harry Houdini's deadliest stunt. She shares how embracing fear, failure and an "amateur’s mindset" transformed her from a cautious child into someone who proves that daredevils aren't born — they're developed.
title: Scared to try something new? Daredevil @MichelleKhare says embrace an amateur’s mindset #TEDTalks
